glittering woman, mother of helios (sun), selene (moon), and eos (dawn)

.SH SUMMARY
ySCORE is a libary to enable operational debugging on a transaction basis by
enumerating a list of checks and data that are then populated as the transation
is processed.  it leads to good overview and quicker trouble shooting.

.SH SERIOUS FOREWARNING
i am a crazy, selfish, dog-fooding c-programmer.  my code tends to be
experimental and constantly evolving.  my point is NOT to be the best, it is
to challenge myself, build from scratch, and allow fast problem solving.

