.SH A) OVERVIEW
after building this easedropping/debugging method into a couple programs,
i decided to standardize, improve, and share the implemenation.  its really
quite simplistic (YMMV).

the only complication for me was that some programs use multiple scorecards
across levels of detail.  to fix this, the interface had to switch to sharing
the <object> across function calls.  once i am happy, i may simplify.

